[Trends of burden on ischemic heart disease and epidemiological transition of 
related risk factors in China, 1990-2017].

[Article in Chinese; Abstract available in Chinese from the publisher]

Wang CR(1), Meng XF(2), Wang CP(3), Liu SW(4).

Author information:
(1)National Center for Women and Children's Health, Chinese Center for Disease 
Control and Prevention, Beijing 100081, China.
(2)Weifang Municipal Center for Disease Control and Prevention, Weifang 261061, 
China.
(3)School of Public Health, Weifang Medical University, Social Health Risk 
Collaborative Innovation Center, "Healthy Shandong" Collaborative Innovation 
Center for Prediction and Governance of Major Social Risks, Weifang 261053, 
