Precision medicine in the era of artificial intelligence: implications in 
chronic disease management.

Subramanian M(1)(2), Wojtusciszyn A(3), Favre L(3), Boughorbel S(4), Shan 
J(2)(5), Letaief KB(6), Pitteloud N(7), Chouchane L(8)(9)(10).

Author information:
